      "originalText": "PK EMP_EMPLOYMENT_ID\nUQ PERSON_ID → EC_PER_PERSON\nUQ USER_ID\nHIRE_DATE (EFFECTIVE_START)\nORIGINAL_START_DATE\nSENIORITY_DATE\nPASS_PROBATION_DATE\nRETIREMENT_DATE\nRESIGNED_DATE (END)\nLAST_DATE_WORKED\nOK_TO_REHIRE\nYEAR_OF_SERVICE\n+ 7 CURRENT_YEARS_IN_*\n+ 7 *_EFFECTIVE_DATE\n+ 20 RESERVE_FIELD",
